  Description: You can exert your unsettling presence to subtly Demoralize others.
    When you do, Demoralize loses the auditory trait and gains the visual trait,
    and you don't take a penalty when you attempt to Demoralize a creature that doesn't
    understand your language. You also gain the Invigorating Fear reaction. Your
    alternate form is a fox, which has the statistics of 1st-level pest form.
